      <title>卢比奥称萨尔瓦多将接受美国罪犯驱逐者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/rubio-says-el-salvador-agrees-to-accept-us-criminal-deportees</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿马尔科·卢比奥周一表示，萨尔瓦多已提出接受来自世界各地的美国罪犯驱逐出境者，其中包括美国公民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/rubio-says-el-salvador-agrees-to-accept-us-criminal-deportees</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 02:15:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将任命拜登宽带计划的批评者来监督该计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/trump-to-tap-critic-of-biden-broadband-plan-to-oversee-program</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据三位知情人士透露，特朗普政府计划提名一位反对前总统乔·拜登 425 亿美元宽带资助计划的人员来监督该计划，这使得该计划的方向受到质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/trump-to-tap-critic-of-biden-broadband-plan-to-oversee-program</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 01:49:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度莫迪受邀下周在白宫会见特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/india-s-modi-invited-to-meet-with-trump-at-white-house-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫官员周一晚间表示，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪已被邀请下周在华盛顿与唐纳德·特朗普总统会面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/india-s-modi-invited-to-meet-with-trump-at-white-house-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 00:47:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普计划与习近平对话，因中国关税期限临近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/trump-plans-to-speak-with-xi-as-deadline-for-china-tariffs-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他的政府计划与中国进行对话，这增加了中国可能暂停征收 10% 关税的可能性。此前，特朗普推迟了对加拿大和墨西哥征收关税的计划，该关税将在数小时后生效。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/trump-plans-to-speak-with-xi-as-deadline-for-china-tariffs-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 00:30:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的关税逆转表明他在贸易问题上大言不惭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/trump-s-tariff-reversal-feeds-reputation-as-paper-tiger-on-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统承诺征收数千亿美元的关税来重塑全球经济，甚至将目标瞄准其最亲密的邻国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/trump-s-tariff-reversal-feeds-reputation-as-paper-tiger-on-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 00:27:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国财政部和 Bessent 因向马斯克提供 DOGE 代币使用权而遭起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/treasury-bessent-sued-over-giving-access-to-musk-s-doge-team</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部被指控违反联邦法律，因为它向伊隆·马斯克的政府效率执法团队提供了大量个人和财务信息的访问权限，从而引发了针对特朗普政府标志性的缩减政府规模举措的法律对决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/treasury-bessent-sued-over-giving-access-to-musk-s-doge-team</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 00:07:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法官拒绝特朗普驳回资金冻结诉讼请求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/judge-extends-block-of-trump-funding-freeze-plan-in-second-delay</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名法官表示，特朗普政府“没有给出任何理由”在进行意识形态审查前不到 24 小时就切断可能高达数万亿美元的联邦拨款、贷款和其他财政援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/judge-extends-block-of-trump-funding-freeze-plan-in-second-delay</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 22:44:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普与加拿大、墨西哥达成边境协议暂时避免贸易战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trudeau-says-trump-tariffs-delayed-30-days-after-call</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国两个邻国同意采取更严厉的措施打击边境移民和贩毒活动后，唐纳德·特朗普总统同意将对加拿大和墨西哥征收 25% 的关税推迟一个月，以暂时避免爆发大陆贸易战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trudeau-says-trump-tariffs-delayed-30-days-after-call</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 21:42:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普任命的华盛顿特区律师提出保护马斯克的 DOGE 员工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trump-appointed-dc-attorney-offers-to-protect-musk-s-doge-staff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国哥伦比亚特区新任临时检察官表示，他将对任何妨碍或威胁伊隆·马斯克政府效率团队的人采取法律行动，在该团队与美国各机构公务员多次发生冲突之后，这一举措的风险进一步上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trump-appointed-dc-attorney-offers-to-protect-musk-s-doge-staff</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 20:54:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪的特朗普策略是迅速做出让步以避免贸易战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/modi-s-trump-strategy-sees-quick-concessions-to-avoid-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了避免一场可能造成毁灭性的贸易战，很少有国家比印度更快地安抚美国总统唐纳德·特朗普。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/modi-s-trump-strategy-sees-quick-concessions-to-avoid-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 15:56:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
